  • Packages that use fr.emse.simulator.world 
    Package Description
    fr.emse.simulator.astar
    This package contains all the utilities for performing a a-star search in a SimulationMap.
    fr.emse.simulator.gui
    This package contains classes for displaying a SimulationMap.
    fr.emse.simulator.world
    This package contains interfaces for the simulation domain: a map containing cells that may be occupied by occupants.
